{"tid":1810881,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍再襲巴格達伊朗勢力　據報擊中民兵車輛","createTime":"2020-01-04T08:40:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-04T09:51:12.000Z","uid":125193,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"33a167f890fa3b81400963a91f75d9058137fcce","tid":1810881,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:40:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500984-20200104.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500984-20200104.htm&d=GO0vWKcqTLT5bpzdAOrPDoR92%2BFrphpe0A3gOlHMrp8%3D&h=983f9049\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1500984-20200104.htm&h=cd5fd76b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1500984-20200104.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n繼日前空襲伊拉克首都巴格達機場、殺死伊朗革命衛隊特種部隊指揮官蘇萊馬尼後，美軍再有針對伊朗舉動。<br />\n<br />\n報道說，美軍向巴格達北部塔吉郊區發動空襲，據報擊中兩架伊拉克什葉派民兵部隊「人民動員」的車輛。「人民動員」被指與伊朗關係密切，長期接受伊朗訓練和支援。<br />\n<br />\n半島電視台引述「人民動員」表示，空襲導致6人死亡，包括救護人員，但否認車隊內有高級指揮官。<br />\n<br />\n伊朗早前就蘇萊馬尼遇襲身亡，揚言會嚴厲報復。"},{"pid":"4e4ea20e02383d29ffbee3892ee46e0e04975ad0","tid":1810881,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"WWIII <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b244d530ba78f26a8ffcd24e0cf6429114133c3","tid":1810881,"uid":78873,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-04T08:42:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.images.express.co.uk/img/dynamic/78/590x/secondary/world-war-3-iran-us-attack-trump-Qassim-Soleimani-2239377.jpg?r=1578060632242\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.express.co.uk%2Fimg%2Fdynamic%2F78%2F590x%2Fsecondary%2Fworld-war-3-iran-us-attack-trump-Qassim-Soleimani-2239377.jpg%3Fr%3D1578060632242&h=18a56c27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ce9c4fc615e712d86a745d2b54c369cd5a9c89b2","tid":1810881,"uid":125193,"li